        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "6658523"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Luistervaardigheid",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Als het goed is heb je gekozen om je luistervaardigheid in het Engels te oefenen.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">De bijbehorende opdracht staat onder het kopje 'Exercise 1'.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Als je vragen hebt, kun je de docent om hulp vragen op Microsoft Teams.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Veel succes!</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\"><strong>Klik op het kopje 'Exercise 1'.</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"text-align-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/d/dde317de9f8f8b412c79548717e2458cd9d69af2.Unknown\" class=\"height-182-pixels width-277-pixels\"/></p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "6659038"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Exercise 1",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Klik op de onderstaande blauwe link om bij de juiste video te komen.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Kijk het filmpje genaamd 'Growing up black in America' helemaal af.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Beantwoord vervolgens de vragen. Schrijf jouw antwoorden op in een schrift!</span></p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "link": "https://www.bbc.co.uk/newsround/32976667",
                            "title": "Growing up black in America - Newsround",
                            "description": "",
                            "comment": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Questions 'Growing up black in America':</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">1. who lives in the White House according to the video?</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">2. What does Adria say about Barack Obama becoming the first black president?</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">3. What does 'segregation' mean according to the video?</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">4. What does Brandon say about the issues between the police and the African-American community?</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">5. How does David feel about the protests?</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">6. Explain: Why was Barack Obama becoming president a special moment in American history?</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "6658524"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Schrijfvaardigheid",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Als het goed is heb je gekozen om je schrijfvaardigheid in het Engels te oefenen.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">De bijbehorende opdracht staat onder het kopje 'Exercise 1'.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Als je vragen hebt, kun je de docent om hulp vragen op Microsoft Teams.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Veel succes!</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\"><strong>Klik op het kopje 'Exercise 1'.</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/1/1ad000a143a7ac7298da8502a8d6f1c333fde78c.jpg\" class=\"height-900-pixels width-1600-pixels\"/></strong></span></p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "6659039"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Exercise 1",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\"><strong>Writing Assignment:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px underline\">'Highschool pupils should have complete freedom to choose their own courses'.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Do you agree or disagree with this prompt? And why?</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Write an essay of approximately 200 words.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">(you may use pen/paper or a computer)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\"><strong>Schrijfopdracht:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px underline\">'Middelbare scholieren moeten het recht krijgen om zelf te kiezen welke lessen ze wel/niet volgen'.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Ben je het wel of niet eens met de volgende stelling? Geef je mening en leg deze uit.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Schrijf een Engelse tekst van ongeveer 200 woorden.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">(je mag de opdracht schrijven of typen)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\"><strong>Als je klaar bent stuur je het document of een foto van je tekst naar Miss. van den Doel via Microsoft Teams.</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        }
                    ],
                    "sections": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "6658535"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Ik ben klaar",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Als het goed is heb je \u00e9\u00e9n van de onderstaande vaardigheden geoefend:</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">- Leesvaardigheid</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">- Luistervaardigheid</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">- Schrijfvaardigheid</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Als je de bijbehorende opdracht(en) hebt afgemaakt, mag je teruggaan naar de online les in Microsoft Teams. Daar vertelt de docent wat je moet doen.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span class=\"font-size-18px\">Je mag deze website nu afsluiten!</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"text-align-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/0/0aaa1d205f1a5adfecf1b246ace946ba9899fae0.jpg\" class=\"height-200-pixels width-400-pixels\"/></p>\n"
                }
            ],
